sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>WhitelistPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>WhitelistedIPListCreateView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>WhitelistedIPDeleteView
    participant SER as WhitelistedIPSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to Whitelist page
    FE->>API1: GET /api/whitelisted-ips/
    API1->>DB: WhitelistedIP.objects.all()
    DB-->>API1: QuerySet[WhitelistedIP]
    API1->>SER: WhitelistedIPSerializer(ips, many=True)
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {whitelisted_ips: [...]}
    FE-->>U: Display whitelist table
    U->>FE: Enter IP address, click "Add to Whitelist"
    FE->>API1: POST /api/whitelisted-ips/ {ip, reason}
    API1->>SER: WhitelistedIPSerializer.validate(data)
    API1->>DB: WhitelistedIP.objects.create(ip=ip, reason=reason)
    DB-->>API1: WhitelistedIP created
    API1-->>FE: 201 Created
    FE-->>U: IP added to whitelist
    U->>FE: Click "Remove" on whitelisted IP
    FE->>API2: DELETE /api/whitelisted-ips/{id}/
    API2->>DB: WhitelistedIP.objects.get(pk=id).delete()
    DB-->>API2: Deleted
    API2-->>FE: 204 No Content
    FE-->>U: IP removed from whitelist
